Package: verywise
Type: Package
Title: Vertex-wise Statistical Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Serena", "Defina", 
            email = "s.defina@erasmusmc.nl", role = c("cre", "aut"), 
            comment = c(ORCID = " 0000-0003-3344-6597")),
    person("Sander", "Lamballais", 
           email = "s.lamballaistessensohn@erasmusmc.n", role = "aut"),
    person("Ryan", "Muetzel", 
           email = "r.muetzel@erasmusmc.nl", role = c("aut", "fnd"))
           )
Maintainer: Serena Defina <s.defina@erasmusmc.nl>
Description: Whole-brain analysis of FreeSurfer MGH format data. The package allows 
  application of several statistical models per vertex, including linear mixed models. 
  It can handle imputed datasets from several packages (mice, mi, amelia, etc.). 
  Multiple testing correction is achieved using MCZ simulations from FreeSurfer.
